divs: sighting detailsthe airspace over nyc as we all know since 911 is very very restricted!!! lately i heard that the wired ny webcam site has spotted strange lights,ufo's,etc...??? so i decided to watch them, well they didn't let me down. almost immediately i saw strange objects,lights,spears,glowing in the sky over either brooklyn,nj or the hudson river in nyc\nj. im am not positive which way these webcams are pointing, so i cant say for sure? but here are some pictures i took off of these cams in particular cams 3 & 4..they seem to catch most of thee action!!! it is pretty strange..they will sometimes stay in one place for a minute or to,other times they appear & zip off quickly...let me know what you think...thanks!!!
